data.description: Price Reduced. Calling all first-time home buyers & investors! Are you in search of your next project or a way to make the most of the winter months? Consider this 1920's craftsman gem w/its inviting covered front porch & the potential to restore it to its original charm & character. Inside you'll find ample space w/the perfect canvas for your renovation ideas. The kitchen is exceptionally roomy & it even features a convenient mudroom that leads to the spacious backyard allowing for outdoor activities & gatherings. Sizable detached garage w/approximately 440 sq ft. You'll appreciate the convenience of both alley access & front access from the main road. Revive history & restore this classic home. Seller will look at reasonable offers.
